<lb ed="ZW" n="0085a08"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0085a09"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pZW06p0085a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">祝
<lb ed="ZW" n="0085a10" type="honorific"/>大明萬萬年刊刻<note n="0085005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「祝大明萬萬年刊刻」，甲本無。</note></p></cb:div>
